WKDocReader is an iOS class for converting Microsoft Word .doc files to NSAttributedStrings.

Supported:

-Bold
-Italic
-Underline style
-Underline color
-Outline
-Text foreground color
-Text background color
-Font
-Font Size
-Superscript/subscript
-Alignment
-Right indent
-Left indent
-First line left indent
-Line spacing
-Paragraph spacing
-Writing direction
-Columns
-Page orientation
-Page size
-Margins
-Is the document read-only
-Should mark spelling/grammar errors
-Default tab interval
-Creation time
-Modification time
-View mode
-View zoom
-View auto-zoom

Unsupported:

-URLs
-Bulleted/numbered lists
-Images/shapes
-Tables (the text  content of a table appears, but not organized into a table.)